name: Airport Transpot Car Duty
description:
It is time to take up an airplane pilot role of an amazing car transporter plane! Airport Transpot Car Duty is one of the latest and most exciting addition to the cargo plane game, it not only gives you a chance to drive an airport cargo truck to transport the car cargo but also lets you be the city plane pilot to master you airplane parking skills.
Features

• Real plane simulator environment.
• Exclusive plane simulator levels
• Unique airplane flight simulator gameplay
• Epic sounds of airplane transporter games
• Full controls of the cargo airplane
